    <div class="post-container" id="fpc-4110754">
                      
		<div class="post" id="post-4110754">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,4110754)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-4110754">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="4203115"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1546799931 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">06 Jan 2019 18:38</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4110754">
									

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers&nbsp;for&nbsp;djkaktus's&nbsp;Proposal&nbsp;III</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>In <em>The Way It Ends</em>, we learn:</p>
<ul>
<li>Aaron was the original O5-1.</li>
<li>Aaron made a deal with Death to bring Sophia back to life. Sophia was the original O5-2.</li>
<li>Vince/Anthony wanted revenge for Aaron's defection.</li>
</ul>
<p>The Epilogue reveals:</p>
<ul>
<li>Calvin is the new O5-1.</li>
<li>Calvin made a deal with Death to bring Olivia back to life. Olivia is now O5-2.</li>
<li>Adam wants revenge for Calvin's defection.</li>
</ul>
<p>We can assume:</p>
<ul>
<li>Olivia (like Sophia) will give the reborn Insurgency a weapon which can destroy the Overseers.</li>
<li>Adam (like Vince) will take part in the effort to kill the new O5s.</li>
<li>The reborn Insurgency (like their predecessors) will successfully kill the new Overseers, but they will not be able to neutralize the Administrator.</li>
<li>The Insurgent with the strongest convictions (like Calvin) will become the new O5-1.</li>
</ul>
<p>djkaktus notes in <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9044427/djkaktus-s-proposal-iii#post-4108185">this comment</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>The only difference [between Aaron and Calvin] is that instead of creating the more hardened but moderating influence of Vince, Calvin creates the radicalizing influence of Adam.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Implying that Adam's convictions may actually be stronger than Vince's.</p>
<p>What does the Broke God call O5-1?</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Heyyyyyy Adam, it's me, Mike.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>

